The paper describes an open-source python library for implementing dynamic selection techniques for classification and ensemble learning. This falls under the broad category of machine learning, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. The most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers topics related to the design and analysis of algorithms for learning from data. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), which are all relevant to the topics covered in the paper.
